title: It might be Jonah Peretti's last chance to turn BuzzFeed around
description: BuzzFeed's stock has fallen below $1 per share and faces the prospect of delisting unless the stock recovers.

title: Workers are secretly using ChatGPT, AI and it will pose big risks for tech leaders
description: Generative AI is seeping into the workplace, whether companies approve of its use or not, and cybersecurity caution is needed with these breakthrough chatbots.

title: Charlie Munger reportedly warns of trouble for the U.S. commercial property market
description: Charlie Munger believes there is trouble ahead for the U.S. commercial property market.

title: A psychologist shares 6 toxic phrases 'highly narcissistic' people always use—and how to deal with them
description: The world is full of difficult personalities, but it's nearly impossible to avoid narcissists. "They are masters of gaslighting," says psychologist and CSU professor Dr. Ramani Durvasula. She shares the phrases that highly narcissists always use — and how to respond.

title: This 28-year-old pays $62 a month to live in a dumpster he built for $5,000—take a look inside
description: After struggling to find an apartment rental in London on a budget, Harrison Marshall turned a dumpster into a tiny home for $5,000. Here's a look inside his "weirdly comfortable" 25-square-foot space, where he now lives for $62 a month.

title: Top cloud providers Amazon, Microsoft and Google face ongoing spending cuts by clients
description: Earnings reports from the leading cloud infrastructure companies showed that businesses continue to look for ways to trim their spending.

title: SpaceX to spend about $2 billion on Starship this year, as Elon Musk pushes to reach orbit
description: Elon Musk expects SpaceX to spend about $2 billion on its Starship rocket development this year, the CEO said on Saturday.
